CGE - Camomile Game Engine

Camomile Game Engine is a 3D graphic software game engine built in standard C.

CGE has been developed mainly for educational purpose. It run most of its features in pure software implementation so that it can easily be run, studied and modified.

CGE depend on SDL for interfacing with hardware.



To run the program

Exemple:
$ ./CGE


